<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
</head>
<body>
<%= image_tag attachments['logo.png'].url %>
<h1>Dear <%= @client.first_name %>,</h1>
  
<p>
You sent a message to <%= @volunteer.first_name %> for help with <%= @program.name %>. Unfortunately, they have not responded.
</p>

<p>
We apologize for the inconvenience. You can continue to wait, or you can message another volunteer by following these steps:
</p>
 
<ol>
<li>Sign in to Tutoria at <a href="https://tutoria.io/en/sign_in">this link</a>.</li>
<br>
<li>Find a new volunteer by going to Search page in the menu.</li>
<br>
<li>In the search results, click the "Message User" button.</li>
</ol>
 
<p>
If you have any questions, please email <a href="mailto:community.manager@tutoria.io">community.manager@tutoria.io</a> or contact +1 (929)359-3986 by phone or WhatsApp.
</p>
  
<p>
Thank you,
</p>
 
<p>
Team Tutoria
</p>
</body>
</html>